1.0.name: wordpress/mat-garganos-baseball-standings
1.0.description: Mat Gargano's Baseball Standings plugin provides you with an easy to use widget that automatically updates on a daily basis that displays the current baseball standings. Each widget is separately configurable to have its own widget title and default division.
